---
// src/components/SeoContent.astro
---
<section class="bg-white py-20 px-8">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Your Challenges. Our Solutions.</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">From warped wood to workflow chaos, these climate-related problems blindside even the best-run projects. Unless you stop them at the gate.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <!-- Time Challenges -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Time</h3>
        <div class="text-left space-y-3">
          <p class="text-gray-600">• Inconsistent site climate warps materials, driving up costs and blowing schedules.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">• Damage triggers rework that pushes every trade's timeline back.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Money Challenges -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Money</h3>
        <div class="text-left space-y-3">
          <p class="text-gray-600">• Climate-controlled units keep materials pristine, cutting pricey replacements.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">• Mobile storage trims handling, warehousing, and damage expenses.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Logistics Challenges -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Logistics</h3>
        <div class="text-left space-y-3">
          <p class="text-gray-600">• Gooseneck trailers drop right on site, freeing workspace for all trades.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">• No more costly shuttles from distant warehouses.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <div class="mt-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Complete Climate Protection Features</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900">Precision Climate Control</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Commercial-grade HVAC + humidifier/de-humidifier lock temperature.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900">Plug-&-Play Power</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">On-board generator with shore-power option means zero reliance on site utilities or half-wired temp poles.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900">Real-Time Monitoring Portal</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Live dashboards, SMS/Email alerts, and HD cameras let you babysit your cargo from your phone, 24/7 nationwide.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-gray-900">Rapid Roll-In Deployment</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We deliver, level, and dial-in climate in under 30 minutes; your crew can load materials the same morning.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

 